## Explore file content with bash commands using and report: 

## How many lines are in the fastq file?

wc -l SRR034310_10pc.fastq 
## 3564012 SRR034310_10pc.fastq

## What is the read length?

cat SRR034310_10pc.fastq | head

@SRR034310.20 4_1_946_1783 length=36
GGTTTGCAGGCAGCAATCGAGTGAAGATCGTTGTGT
+
IIIIIII8HIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIII
@SRR034310.34 4_1_1204_1643 length=36
GGAATGCAGGAGGAGCTGATGGGATTGTCTGGAGAA
+
IIIIIII6@@IIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIII
@SRR034310.42 4_1_1264_1607 length=36
GGTTTGCAGGAGAGAGTTACAGGAGTCCAGGAGGGA

# la longueur des read est de 36 nuclééotides !

##How many barcodes are in Details_Barcode_Population_SRR034310?

cat Details_Barcode_Population_SRR034310.txt | head

CCCC	BearPaw1
CCAA	BearPaw2
CCTT	BearPaw3
CCGG	BearPaw4
CACA	BearPaw5
CAAC	BearPaw6
CATG	BearPaw7
CAGT	BearPaw8
CTCT	RabbitSlough1
